article.description: — Gibson Jimerson tossed in 18 points, Marten Linssen scored 15 and Saint Louis rolled to an 86-44 victory over Eastern Illinois in nonconference action on Friday night.
article.headline: Saint Louis breezes to 86-44 victory over Eastern Illinois
article.linkText: Saint Louis breezes to 86-44 victory over Eastern Illinois
article.story: ST. LOUIS -- — Gibson Jimerson tossed in 18 points, Marten Linssen scored 15 and Saint Louis rolled to an 86-44 victory over Eastern Illinois in nonconference action on Friday night. Yuri Collins finished with 11 points and six assists for the Billikens (3-0), while Francis Okoro came off the bench to score 11 and grab 12 rebounds. Reserve CJ Lane had 10 points to lead the Panthers (0-2), who made just 13 of 50 shots from the floor. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25------ Information from: Automated Insights, http://automatedinsights.com/ ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
